	•	LTI (Latent Trajectory Interpreter): WRTJ is a perceptual artifact of LTI operation
	•	CIWS metaphor: lock → track → intercept
	•	Language-as-attractor: trajectories converge toward attractor basins
	•	Compression doctrine: smaller inputs define larger structures

